					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>BTW am I right that it's another of those things that feed on the subject's emotions? The test logs as well as its pursuit of satisfying its &quot;clients&quot; makes me suspect it to be the case.</p> </blockquote> <p>Not really. It just wants to have a good time, and is happy when the people it &quot;dates&quot; are satisfyed. That's why it gets sad when one of the subjects scream at it.</p> 
